songs.title: No Hook
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
One take, one take gang
One take, one take gang
One take, one take gang
One take, one take gang
Hey, 999
One take one take gang (Fuck my mans the low, hoe)
Ya dig?

[Verse]
Heard you fucked my mans on the low, ho (Woo!)
For some tickets to my Chicago show, ho (Front row)
I've been balling on these hoes, feel like Michael (Swish)
Ayy, baby keep that on the low though (The low, the low, the low) Ayy, huh, ayy, bands on me got more dope (Cash)
Huh, ayy, I'm a dragon boy you a Komodo (You know what I mean)
Pose, huh, yeah, life's a photo (Splash)
Huh, ayy, pull up on the scene with my bros (Gang)
Runnin' through the 6 like my woes, Drake (Head)
Pockets fat, look like Ricky Rozay, huh (Head)
Money on deck, baby, okay, huh (Rich)
I ain't savin' hoes, baby, no way, huh (Bitch)
Ayy, huh, 90 on the e-way
500k for my car, so it's not the freeway (Skrrt, skrrt)
I remember scamming Bathing Ape on Ebay (I was broke)
Now I'm finna go to Bathing Ape with 10k
I don't even like that shit no more, It's all about Murakami (Yeah)
I say that shit right, it's not Murakami, baby girl, you should find it
Huh, I've been ballin' super hard baby, I'm a ballaholic, huh
Slash alcoholic, huh, slash percaholic, huh, slash percules
Pray to god these drugs ain't hurtin' me (Amen)
Ayy, uh, gun on my hip so I'm not worried (Amen)
I got a 30, would it be cliche for me to say Stephen Curry, huh, ya dig?
Ayy, keep on vibin'
Listenin' to 21 Pilots (Bow)
Not they new shit, they old shit, that cold shit (Ya dig?)
I've been ballin' like Sosa, you know this (Tryna party)
Ayy, huh, ayy, huh, get money everyday (cash)
Lady Gaga with that choppa, it got a poker face (Pew pew pew)
Fuck your bitch, I poke her face (Bitch)
Bust on her face, you know that shit disgrace (Uh)
